我想返去。」C朗強調自己所有資產都公開，根本冇可能有隱瞞：「我係一本任人揭嘅書，上Google打我個名已經有齊所有資料，好似《福布斯》就將我所有收入都列晒出嚟啦！」 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n究竟C朗係一時意氣定黎真呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n踢熱刺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nFF下好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d9c9ce1de644656349fd5c51e3eac61f7cd249b","tid":347872,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:42:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係佢就踢利記，係西甲拎冠都拎到悶，幫利記拎冠先叻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幫利定阿拎聯賽歐聯威啲？"},{"pid":"9319c6b46143675bd5e5f20b77c06cebc2ecb578","tid":347872,"uid":3244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:45:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29f09fe00b1a8673b8c90f75c714a28bab56f107","tid":347872,"uid":6782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T10:34:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>傳完尼馬 又傳番C朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n記者唔洗開飯咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e27095d0afda9c95c9af97fbb851b96bc4d0515","tid":347872,"uid":124087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T12:28:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係返英國都唔撚返最聯啦<br />\n成班最迷又想打J牙？收皮啦柒頭</blockquote><br />\n除左曼聯有邊隊會要佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n傳最聯同最聯抬價部"},{"pid":"d3b5e54b8ae0e9a2420e976f521aa378610275e8","tid":347872,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T12:30:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dad1a5bf6f1a5aeae3dfb89fe97d789cb86352fc","tid":347872,"uid":5006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T12:38:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>C朗被指涉嫌逃稅1,470萬歐元，案件近日喺西班牙進行審理，而周一佢同法官莫妮卡高美絲進行私人聆訊，照計內容係保密，但Cadena Ser電台就好把炮咁收到料。根據呢間電台嘅報道，指C朗向法官有以下言論：「我喺英格蘭（效力曼聯）期間，從未遇過有關稅務問題，呢個亦係我希望返去英格蘭嘅原因。」<br />\n<br />\n咁睇C朗要離開皇馬嘅想法仍然冇變過，皇馬肯放佢走亦要先刮返最後一大筆錢先，有冇球會願意畀天價轉會費收購C朗係一大疑問。尼馬以2億英鎊離隊，但佢正值當打，C朗始終已經32歲，冇人知佢仲有幾多年可以交出一季入四五十球嘅表現。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170805&amp;guid=57043673&amp;category_guid=7032049&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170805%26guid%3D57043673%26category_guid%3D7032049%26category%3Dinstant&d=RteHjx9wNTTgmW3pMpHAc0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=833ce899\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170805%26guid%3D57043673%26category_guid%3D7032049%26category%3Dinstant&h=63ec7bb9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170805&amp;guid=57043673&amp;category_guid=7032049&amp;category=instant</a></blockquote><br />\nC朗而家就算表現有少少回落都屌打歐洲其他一線前鋒，除非大傷，以佢身體條件起碼仲有3,4年貨賣，係之前推到個standard太高，退多步去到30幾球一季，計埋通脹，過億買都抵到爛啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/05/203815_a34ecbb7149763625e75f8d56f5b273f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F05%2F203815_a34ecbb7149763625e75f8d56f5b273f.jpg&h=55bb1a52&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/05/203817_7042915f4c12066e9bd185bfeac955c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F05%2F203817_7042915f4c12066e9bd185bfeac955c8.jpg&h=3f56e29f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a524f93717a2be8b929c6f84a204390d4aff42b","tid":347872,"uid":72946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T13:04:01.000Z","msg":"C&gt;m&gt;n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9414ee0ff812fbd91736002fa1d2291116505fc0","