 /></blockquote><br />\n14嗰季小花企喺到踢波，但個數據好似都歐洲第二，牙朗企喺到踢波都應該拎到英超神射手，一季3,40球"},{"pid":"1db2b53f6fa1e034514cf957bf23088d6bb99a25","tid":347872,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T13:57:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曼聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n牙朗係反摩大隊其中一員wor。"},{"pid":"3fa57f6f1388fd460e5b65dedb7534d913d16629","tid":347872,"uid":38482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T14:12:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>C朗被指涉嫌逃稅1,470萬歐元，案件近日喺西班牙進行審理，而周一佢同法官莫妮卡高美絲進行私人聆訊，照計內容係保密，但Cadena Ser電台就好把炮咁收到料。根據呢間電台嘅報道，指C朗向法官有以下言論：「我喺英格蘭（效力曼聯）期間，從未遇過有關稅務問題，呢個亦係我希望返去英格蘭嘅原因。」<br />\n<br />\n咁睇C朗要離開皇馬嘅想法仍然冇變過，皇馬肯放佢走亦要先刮返最後一大筆錢先，有冇球會願意畀天價轉會費收購C朗係一大疑問。尼馬以2億英鎊離隊，但佢正值當打，C朗始終已經32歲，冇人知佢仲有幾多年可以交出一季入四五十球嘅表現。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170805&amp;guid=57043673&amp;category_guid=7032049&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170805%26guid%3D57043673%26category_guid%3D7032049%26category%3Dinstant&d=RteHjx9wNTTgmW3pMpHAc0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=833ce899\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170805%26guid%3D57043673%26category_guid%3D7032049%26category%3Dinstant&h=63ec7bb9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170805&amp;guid=57043673&amp;category_guid=7032049&amp;category=instant</a></blockquote><br />\n天地有正氣，我朗絕對冇逃稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95bf06078e13e3ffa6ab2609f4793d38824bb238","tid":347872,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T14:25:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>C朗被指涉嫌逃稅1,470萬歐元，案件近日喺西班牙進行審理，而周一佢同法官莫妮卡高美絲進行私人聆訊，照計內容係保密，但Cadena Ser電台就好把炮咁收到料。根據呢間